title: The Art of Greece and Rome (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Cambridge University Press | 2004 | 0521540372 | Eng | 194 p | PDF | 30.7 MB

Susan Woodford illuminates the great achievements of classical art and architecture and conveys a sense of the excitement that inspired the creative artists of the ancient world. Examining all aspects of Greek and Roman visual arts, this revised edition includes a new chapter on Roman architecture, as well as new illustrations, and an updated bibliography and glossary
